The Spiritual Director of Adoration Ministry, Enugu, Rev. Fr. Ejike Mbaka, has gifted a new car to gospel singer, Gozie Okeke. The gospel singer took to his Instagram page on Monday to share the video of himself inside the car. A voice in the video stated that the gift was from the popular reverend father to the singer. The singer captioned the video, “All I have to say is thank you Jesus, My father in the Lord Rev Fr. Ejike Mbaka. You will hear from me soon. May God keep you for me in the name of Jesus Christ Amen. I love you with passion.” See video below:  Copyright PUNCH. All rights reserved. This material, and other digital content on this website, may not be reproduced, published, broadcast, rewritten or redistributed in whole or in part without prior express written permission from PUNCH. Contact: theeditor@punchng.com